OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776438666
OL,3,CPeople living in vehicles and caravans
OL,4,Con Bristol's Downs have 21 days to
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FPeople living in vehicles and caravans
OL,8,Fon the Downs in Bristol will have to
OL,9,Fleave in the next few weeks or risk
OL,10,Farrest.
OL,12,FThe biggest single development in a
OL,13,Fsaga lasting years came following a
OL,14,Fcourt order giving Bristol City
OL,15,FCouncil the power to force those
OL,16,Fliving on roads surrounding the famous
OL,17,Fopen space to move on.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776438666
OL,3,CPeople living in vehicles and caravans
OL,4,Con Bristol's Downs have 21 days to
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FThe possession order will take affect
OL,8,Ffrom the next 21 days, after which the
OL,9,Fpowers of arrest will be permissible
OL,10,Fas a last resort.
OL,12,FThe council says it will continue to
OL,13,Ftalk to van dwellers to offer them
OL,14,Falternatives to living on the roadside.
OL,16,FIt is estimated 43 vehicles remain on
OL,17,Fthe Downs, a dramatic reduction on the
OL,18,Fnumbers there at the peak of the
OL,19,Fencampment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776438666
OL,3,CPeople living in vehicles and caravans
OL,4,Con Bristol's Downs have 21 days to
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FAt Bristol County Court today (April
OL,8,F16) the council's legal
OL,9,Frepresentative, Robin Denford, said
OL,10,Fpossession of the Downs was necessary
OL,11,F'to protect the public of Bristol from
OL,12,Ffurther trespass and to control anti-
OL,13,Fsocial behaviour'.
OL,15,FIt's long been claimed that without a
OL,16,Fpublic toilet block open 24 hours a
OL,17,Fday, people living in the vans have
OL,18,Fused nearby hedges and woods as a
OL,19,Ftoilet, creating a risk to public
OL,20,Fhealth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776438666
OL,3,CPeople living in vehicles and caravans
OL,4,Con Bristol's Downs have 21 days to
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FThe court was told the Council has 79
OL,8,Fplaces at six 'meanwhile' sites for
OL,9,Fvan dwellers to access toilets, water
OL,10,Fand electricity. They pay a fee as
OL,11,Fwell as Band A council tax to remain
OL,12,Funtil a more permanent housing
OL,13,Fsolution is found.
OL,15,FDistrict Judge John Napier said he
OL,16,Fwould now consider a Council
OL,17,Fapplication for an injunction to
OL,18,Fprevent anyone returning to the Downs
OL,19,Fto live.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776438666
OL,3,CPeople living in vehicles and caravans
OL,4,Con Bristol's Downs have 21 days to
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FAfter the hearing, the campaign group
OL,8,F'Protect The Downs' welcomed the
OL,9,Fdevelopment. Alan told ITV News: "It's
OL,10,Fnot a victory for anybody. Hundreds of
OL,11,Fpeople are living in vans in 2026.
OL,13,F"But we are happier now that the
OL,14,FCouncil has come on board and accepted
OL,15,Fthe issues we raised over a year ago
OL,16,Fnow and accept their responsibilities."
OL,18,FBut those defending the van dwellers
OL,19,Fsay the Council is choosing the power
OL,20,Fof arrest over its responsibility to
OL,21,Fhouse people.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776438666
OL,3,CPeople living in vehicles and caravans
OL,4,Con Bristol's Downs have 21 days to
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,F"The Council has been playing 'Whack a
OL,8,FMole' with the travellers in the city
OL,9,Ffor at leats 15 years," said a
OL,10,Fspokesperson for Bristol Housing
OL,11,FAction. "They evict from one site and
OL,12,Fthey pop up somewhere else.
OL,14,F"What they need to do is find a
OL,15,Fpermanent solution to find lots of
OL,16,Fsites, reasonably close to the city
OL,17,Fcentre, where they can put caravans
OL,18,Fand vehicles, but they don't want to
OL,19,Fdo that because they know it will
OL,20,Fattract more travellers to the city."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
